The [[Allmusic]] review awarded the album 4 stars stating "The music is typically swinging and has its exciting moments".<ref name="Allmusic">Yanow, S., [http://www.allmusic.com/album/new-horizons-mw0000920445 Allmusic Review] accessed April 24, 2014</ref>

